green\")\r\n\r\nfor row in range(20):\r\n    table.add_row(*[f\"{row}-{i}\" for i in columns])\r\n\r\nconsole = Console()\r\n\r\nstart = time.time()\r\nconsole.print(table)\r\ntotal = time.time() - start\r\nconsole.print(f\"[red]This took {total:.2f} seconds\")\r\n```\r\n\r\nInside the vscode console (Windows 10): `This took 1.29 seconds`\r\n\r\nIn regular shell (Windows 10 / Ubuntu): `This took 0.10 seconds`\r\n\r\nIt seems that the issue comes from using colors. Without style, the table renders much faster under vscode (0.2 seconds).\r\n\r\nI realize this probably isn't a high-priority issue, but I thought you might like to know!\r\n\r\nP.S. Great library, I just discovered it and it's a lot of fun! I wish I could use it to replace everything prompt-toolkit does","closed_by":{"login":"erezsh","id":731464,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjczMTQ2NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/731464?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh","html_url":"https://github.com/erezsh","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/erezsh/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"performed_via_github_app":null}